From: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
Date: Wed, 3 Apr 2024 16:29:14 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Revert "workqueue: Implement system-wide nr_active
 enforcement for unbound workqueues"
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.8.4
Git-commit: 9349100ccf3314d304b9522c711c3feeb06e5b79

This reverts commit 843288afd3cc6f3342659c6cf81fc47684d25563 which is commit
5797b1c18919cd9c289ded7954383e499f729ce0 upstream.

